{
  "texts": [
    "We applied the SambaNova Platform (https://sambanova.ai/) to implement the full Llama 3.1 70B and 405B models.",
    "Here, we used the Llama 3.1 models to extract information for the 10 Pennsylvania well records only.",
    "Our results showed an improved performance when Llama 3.1 models were used.",
    "Specifically, the values of AOS for location and depth reached 80% and 90% with the Llama 3.1 70B model, and 90% and 100% with the Llama 3.1 405B model.",
    "The Llama 3.1 405B model extracted all correct depth information, including the case with a depth of \"0\"."
  ]
}